  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t各位同志好，我覺得隨著最近反動派越來越猖獗的輿論宣傳衝擊下，革命情操開始冷淡，所以我特地拿出這些寶貴的資料給大家分享，大家務必牢記使命，不忘初心，從而能更好的掃清一切資本主義的殘留，暴風驟雨一樣打擊反動派，黨的光芒像太陽一樣照耀著每個人！讓反革命無處藏身！<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGZjMjM0NGIxMjAwOWRhMDQ2YjdjLmpwZz93aWR0aD01NjQmaGVpZ2h0PTg3NA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dfc2344b12009da046b7c.jpg?width=564&amp;height=874\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dfc2344b12009da046b7c.jpg?width=564&amp;height=874\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dfc2344b12009da046b7c.jpg?width=564&amp;height=874\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n偉大的革命導師領導著我們前進！！！<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGM2ODZmY2YwMjZhOWVjYmQ2MGU5LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4c686fcf026a9ecbd60e9.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4c686fcf026a9ecbd60e9.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4c686fcf026a9ecbd60e9.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGExMDVkMDRjODI1NWM4Y2Y1NTY3LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/da105d04c8255c8cf5567.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/da105d04c8255c8cf5567.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/da105d04c8255c8cf5567.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYThjNDBjN2RlMWUwZDIxMGM4OTNhLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a8c40c7de1e0d210c893a.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a8c40c7de1e0d210c893a.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a8c40c7de1e0d210c893a.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvY2E2Y2YzYmI1ZjQwYTg1NTRhNWUzLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ca6cf3bb5f40a8554a5e3.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ca6cf3bb5f40a8554a5e3.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ca6cf3bb5f40a8554a5e3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYWQ4ZTM5ZDZmNTE4NTEzNmIyNDBmLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ad8e39d6f5185136b240f.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ad8e39d6f5185136b240f.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ad8e39d6f5185136b240f.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n火車進站出站都要高喊革命萬歲！！！<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMmI4NDQxZWZjOTI5ZDI4OGM5MmQ0LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2b8441efc929d288c92d4.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2b8441efc929d288c92d4.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2b8441efc929d288c92d4.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTA0MTJlMTY5NGVkYmZkYTc1NWQ3LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDU4JmhlaWdodD02NDI\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e0412e1694edbfda755d7.jpg?width=1058&amp;height=642\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e0412e1694edbfda755d7.jpg?width=1058&amp;height=642\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e0412e1694edbfda755d7.jpg?width=1058&amp;height=642\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoIC9maWxlLzRiNjNkZWEyMTI1NDFjYzdmMWNmMC5qcGc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph /file/4b63dea212541cc7f1cf0.jpg\">https://telegra.ph /file/4b63dea212541cc7f1cf0.jpg</a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGI2M2RlYTIxMjU0MWNjN2YxY2YwLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDI0JmhlaWdodD02ODM\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4b63dea212541cc7f1cf0.jpg?width=1024&amp;height=683\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4b63dea212541cc7f1cf0.jpg?width=1024&amp;height=683\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4b63dea212541cc7f1cf0.jpg?width=1024&amp;height=683\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMDRjM2I1ZWI1ZmRlOTI3OGVjYThkLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMzYwJmhlaWdodD0yMTU3\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/04c3b5eb5fde9278eca8d.jpg?width=1360&amp;height=2157\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/04c3b5eb5fde9278eca8d.jpg?width=1360&amp;height=2157\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/04c3b5eb5fde9278eca8d.jpg?width=1360&amp;height=2157\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYWM4ZDZhYmFmZGI1MmM1MTgzNmFiLmpwZz93aWR0aD05MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTYyNw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ac8d6abafdb52c51836ab.jpg?width=900&amp;height=627\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ac8d6abafdb52c51836ab.jpg?width=900&amp;height=627\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ac8d6abafdb52c51836ab.jpg?width=900&amp;height=627\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvM2MxNmJkOTJjNWVhZWQ2ZGIzNjE2LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDcwJmhlaWdodD0xNjAw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3c16bd92c5eaed6db3616.jpg?width=1070&amp;height=1600\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3c16bd92c5eaed6db3616.jpg?width=1070&amp;height=1600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3c16bd92c5eaed6db3616.jpg?width=1070&amp;height=1600\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n十月革命一聲炮響給我們帶來了社會主義！<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGY1ZjYwNWVkMGRmMGZmMjhiMjE3LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDY3JmhlaWdodD0xNjAw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0f5f605ed0df0ff28b217.jpg?width=1067&amp;height=1600\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0f5f605ed0df0ff28b217.jpg?width=1067&amp;height=1600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0f5f605ed0df0ff28b217.jpg?width=1067&amp;height=1600\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n世界人民大團結，推翻萬惡的資本主義，打碎資本家的枷鎖！砸爛資產階級的意識形態！<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n中蘇友誼萬古長青！<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMjkzYjRkYTJlNmVjZDkyMDhiYTg0LnBuZz93aWR0aD00MjEmaGVpZ2h0PTU1MA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/293b4da2e6ecd9208ba84.png?width=421&amp;height=550\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/293b4da2e6ecd9208ba84.png?width=421&amp;height=550\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/293b4da2e6ecd9208ba84.png?width=421&amp;height=550\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n革命是光榮的，人民是偉大的！<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYWEzYzZhMzgwYjVjODMzZGQ0YzZjLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMjgxJmhlaWdodD0yMTU3\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/aa3c6a380b5c833dd4c6c.jpg?width=1281&amp;height=2157\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/aa3c6a380b5c833dd4c6c.jpg?width=1281&amp;height=2157\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/aa3c6a380b5c833dd4c6c.jpg?width=1281&amp;height=2157\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjE5ZTAwOTAzNzg0MjE4MjU4NDY1LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMjA2JmhlaWdodD0xNzIy\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b19e00903784218258465.jpg?width=1206&amp;height=1722\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b19e00903784218258465.jpg?width=1206&amp;height=1722\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b19e00903784218258465.jpg?width=1206&amp;height=1722\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZjJlZGIzMGYxNTdhNzZhZGI5OWE1LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xODAwJmhlaWdodD0xNDQw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f2edb30f157a76adb99a5.jpg?width=1800&amp;height=1440\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f2edb30f157a76adb99a5.jpg?width=1800&amp;height=1440\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f2edb30f157a76adb99a5.jpg?width=1800&amp;height=1440\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTc3NTY2YTNlZTM5NTM4MDcwNWQwLmpwZz93aWR0aD0yMDAwJmhlaWdodD0xNjk2\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/977566a3ee395380705d0.jpg?width=2000&amp;height=1696\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/977566a3ee395380705d0.jpg?width=2000&amp;height=1696\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/977566a3ee395380705d0.jpg?width=2000&amp;height=1696\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n同時要注意了，培養社會主義接班人要從小孩子做起，品學兼優的小孩，6歲就要進行社會主義教育，有主人翁意識，要清楚階級鬥爭，要對反革命和反動派毫不留情，哪怕是父母或者是兄弟，因為外國代理人時時刻刻會想著推翻革命，所以需要時刻準備著！！！12歲就要知道自己對祖國母親的義務，當祖國和黨召喚的時候，就需要義無反顧，獻出自己的身體甚至是生命！為了祖國母親獻出自己最寶貴的東西是至高無上的榮耀，說明了烈火中鑄成的鋼鐵意志！<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMzNjNDZhMWNjNWM3YzMzMWNkMWFmLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDIwJmhlaWdodD02MTQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/33c46a1cc5c7c331cd1af.jpg?width=1020&amp;height=614\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/33c46a1cc5c7c331cd1af.jpg?width=1020&amp;height=614\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/33c46a1cc5c7c331cd1af.jpg?width=1020&amp;height=614\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGM2NjViMzhhODI3ZWE0NjU0Yzk5LnBuZz93aWR0aD0yMDEmaGVpZ2h0PTMwMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0c665b38a827ea4654c99.png?width=201&amp;height=300\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0c665b38a827ea4654c99.png?width=201&amp;height=300\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0c665b38a827ea4654c99.png?width=201&amp;height=300\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n對於教育祖國兒童，未來的花朵，<br/>\n<br/>\r\n哪怕晚上睡覺，也不能放棄愛國主義教育，內褲和被子的花紋都要充滿了對革命的熱情，你看啊，<br/>\n<br/>\r\n我們的蘇維埃祖國革命開始被帝國主義圍剿，他們給反動派的坦克，都是敵人送給我們的禮物！我們奪去，才能進行更好的抗爭！<br/>\n<br/>\r\n（注：英國產的Mark V坦克，大多數毀於戰爭或被拆毀，現存大多數Mark V在前蘇聯地區）<br/>\n<br/>\r\n在這樣的美夢裡入睡，是多麼的幸福！革命先輩無處不在，陪伴著我們日日夜夜，連內褲上都是！我們一刻都不能分離！我們心系祖國，心系革命，時刻準備著！<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNmU1OTBiZWIxYjU5NzY5MzFmYTg4LnBuZz93aWR0aD04MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTcwMw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6e590beb1b5976931fa88.png?width=800&amp;height=703\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6e590beb1b5976931fa88.png?width=800&amp;height=703\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6e590beb1b5976931fa88.png?width=800&amp;height=703\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n偉大的列寧同志指導著我們學習成長，成為國家的棟樑！<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMDY1NDcwNTcwMDRkYmM2Y2E1OTZlLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMjgwJmhlaWdodD0xNzYy\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/06547057004dbc6ca596e.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=1762\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/06547057004dbc6ca596e.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=1762\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/06547057004dbc6ca596e.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=1762\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n各位同志，祝你們生活愉快，過一個革命化的一天，每天都充滿了精神的追求和崇高的意義！<br/>\n<br/>\r\n革命萬歲！！！\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
